a}-\\epi$), and $L_{iso}-\\epi$ relations is statistically real but\nstrongly influenced by so far uncalibrated GRB detector thresholds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Apr 2009 06:37:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Mar 2010 03:31:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 3 Nov 2011 20:32:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-11-07"}
