ke free\nstanding layers, edge structures of ribbons, topological defects, or mechanical\nand chemical properties were not covered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Apr 2009 12:40:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-04-10"}
